data.description: Welcome to this 3BR/1.5BA home on a private lot in the desirable North end of Staunton.  Comfortable layout with two living spaces on the first floor and tons of natural light throughout.  Large, fenced yard for pets and several landscaped outdoor entertaining areas.  Try out the Nest Smart Home App including wireless keypad entry, front and back yard cameras and thermostat.  New HVAC in 2018 and Radon mitigation system in basement.  Minutes to all that downtown Staunton has to offer.  Short drive to I81/I64, perfect for commuters.  Don't let this one pass you by!
